<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Calendar" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Calendar,</orth> 1) almanac: <bibl n="shak. err 5.404" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 404</bibl> (cf. <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 41</bibl>). <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.86" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 86</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.276" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 276</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 134</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.1.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 1, 58</bibl>.<lb />2) note-book, record: <cit><quote>the care I have had to even your content, I wish might be found in the c. of my past endeavours,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he is the card or c. of gentry,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 114</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>